          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Workforce Recovery and Training Services Act of 2020 </b></p> <p>This bill establishes a grant program for states to provide employment training services to adults and dislocated workers. Of these funds, a specified amount must be allocated to areas most significantly impacted by the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-07-22T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
